{
  "texts": [
    "This experiment assessed the effectiveness of chunkers in retrieving relevant documents for a given query.",
    "We used 10 datasets, shown in Tables 1 and 4.",
    "Most documents on the BEIR benchmark (Thakur et al., 2021) are too short for chunking to be effective.",
    "To address this, we synthesized longer documents by stitching short documents from six datasets where documents are too short (see Appendix C for details).",
    "We randomly sampled 100 queries from each dataset and retrieved the top k chunks, where k ∈ [1, 3, 5, 10]."
  ]
}